K mart Corp said its sales for thefive weeks ended April One rose 4.6 pct to 2.18 billion dlrsfrom 2.08 billion dlrs a year earlier. On a comparable storebasis, sales rose one-tenth of one pct.    It said year-to-date sales increased 7.9 pct to 3.64billion dlrs from 3.37 billion dlrs in the same 1986 period. Ona comparable store basis, the increase was 3.2 pct. Reuter&#3;